title: This week's top selling songs and albums on Apple's iTunes
text:
The Canadian Press - ONLINE EDITION This week's top selling songs and albums on Apple's iTunes By: The Associated Press 
iTunes' Official Music Charts for the week ending Oct. 8, 2015: 
Top Songs 
2. The Hills, The Weeknd 
3. Stitches, Shawn Mendes 
4. Wildest Dreams, Taylor Swift 
5. What Do You Mean?, Justin Bieber 
6. Downtown (feat. Eric Nally, Me., Macklemore & Ryan Lewis 
7. Ex's & Oh's, Elle King 
8. 679 (feat. Monty), Fetty Wap 
9. Locked Away (feat. Adam Levine), R. City 
10. Can't Feel My Face, The Weeknd 
Top Albums 
1. What a Time To Be Alive, Drake & Future 
2. Unbreakable, Janet Jackson 
3. Beauty Behind the Madness, The Weeknd 
4. Calling All Lovers, Tamar Braxton 
5. Fetty Wap, Fetty Wap 
6. 1989, Taylor Swift 
7. Cold Beer Conversation, George Strait 
8. Tangled Up, Thomas Rhett 
9. T R A P S O U L, Bryson Tiller
